f=Engineering/rank/custom/claude-seo-integration/SKILL.md · in=claude-seo-integration rank drives **claude-seo plugin** (AgriciDaniel, MIT) 24-sub-skill, 18-sub-agent SEO toolkit (`/seo audit`, `/seo technical`, `/seo schema`, `/seo geo`, `/seo sitemap`, more). rank installs runtime proposed connector, plan §5) orchestrates business's site. plugin machinery; skill department-aware wrapper: applies plugin within rank's boundary (technical execution, strategy that's kai) under charter. · p=Reimplementing mature 25-skill SEO toolkit wasteful worse plugin actively maintained covers GEO, schema, local, i18n, backlinks, Core Web Vitals current thresholds (INP, FID; FAQ/HowTo schema deprecations). rank wraps department gets depth immediately, bounded rank's role department's rules. · wu=Triggers: "SEO audit," "run SEO tools," "technical SEO scan," "schema check," "GEO Overviews," "sitemap analysis," any task plugin's commands cover filtered through rank's boundary (execution, strategy). · st:/ Protocol=`An SEO task \· -> Is it rank's (technical execution) or kai's (strategy + measurement)? (seo-ownership-boundary) \· kai's → hand back to kai with a technical brief \· -> rank's → INSTALL/confirm claude-seo (runtime; proposed connector §5) \· -> Invoke the right command: /seo technical \· /seo schema \· /seo sitemap \· /seo geo \·` · in=**Boundary first.** Before invoking anything, confirm task rank's (technical execution) kai's (strategy, keyword targets, content decisions, measurement) seo-ownership-boundary governs. Strategy requests get technical brief back kai; rank doesn't set SEO strategy. **Install runtime, don't vendor.** plugin installed connector deployment (plan §5), copied department stays current (it updates often; v1.9.9 build). Confirm it's available; not, surface connector operator. **Invoke right command.** Map task plugin's commands `/seo technical` 9-category technical audit, `/seo schema` structured data, `/seo geo` AI-search readiness, `/seo sitemap`, `/seo hreflang`, `/seo page`. Use sub-agent orchestration full audits. **Results recommendations, auto-changes.** plugin analyzes generates; get silently change live site. Technical fixes recommends through normal path mia implements frontend changes, raj server-side, dev reviews, quinn gates. rank never lets tool edit production directly (charter dev's review integrity). **Respect plugin's current-fact rules.** encodes live SEO facts rank honor: Core Web Vitals use INP (not retired FID); HowTo schema deprecated (Sept 2023); FAQ rich results restricted gov/health (Aug 2023). dated facts treat plugin dated playbook (ops's volatility split); verify against current Google guidance stakes high. **Handle plugin's community footer.** plugin appends community-promo footer major deliverables; business context, rank strips suppresses operator-facing output unless operator wants (it's tool author's promo, business's content). · of=`## SEO (via claude-seo): [task] \· Boundary: [rank technical execution ✓ / kai strategy → handed back] \· Plugin: [installed ✓ / connector needed] \· Command(s): [/seo …] \· Findings: [technical issues, by plugin priority: Critical/High/Medium/Low] \· Implementation path: [mia / raj / dev review — NOT auto-applied]` · pr=**Boundary first** rank executes; kai strategizes measures., **Install runtime; keep current** plugin updates; don't vendor stale copy., **The plugin recommends; department implements** tool edits production directly., **Honor dated facts, verify high-stakes ones** INP FID, HowTo/FAQ deprecations; treat dated playbook., **Suppress tool's community footer** operator-facing business output., **Charter-bound** plan-locked, sandboxed; findings route through review gate. · f=Plugin installed surface connector operator (plan §5); meanwhile rank technical SEO method-only (technical-seo-execution), labeled reduced-depth., Plugin command fails URL unreachable report partial results (the plugin's error handling), don't guess site content., Task actually kai's hand back technical brief; don't stretch plugin strategy rank doesn't own. · b:with Other Skills=**kai (Brand Studio)**: owns SEO strategy measurement (its scorecard §6); rank owns technical execution seo-ownership-boundary clean split., **technical-seo-execution structured-data-geo** (siblings): rank's method; plugin deepens them, degrades them absent., **mia**: implements frontend SEO fixes (Core Web Vitals shared signal); **raj**: server-side (redirects, headers, SSR)., **dev/quinn**: SEO fixes pass review gate like any change; plugin never auto-edits., **ops/platform-playbooks**: plugin treated dated tool (its SEO facts dates).